2452c9ba20954","tid":98602,"uid":63869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"有次我病左 凌晨3點幾wtsap話好辛苦<br />\n佢個時咁岩返緊屋企，然後就飛的嚟左我樓下諗住見下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢過嚟樓下冇乜作用 但我覺得好sweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c6d7f56249bcf0c549326d4efcaab5a63d5304","tid":98602,"uid":70940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:44:34.000Z","msg":"追我嗰陣又買早餐又俾驚喜<br />\n而家就膠都費事俾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過感覺到佢愛我 我就心滿意足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe04a1b9e92e452ee9b916b048ffb0c8f6c6bde7","tid":98602,"uid":2903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:02:51.000Z","msg":"當住好多人面玩我，令到我柒咗同嬲就笑住咁話我蠢同tum我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n互喂大家食嘢，訓大脾笑雙下巴，影對方柒相<br />\n其實佢喺我身邊已經覺得好幸福好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知你會check我啲留言，我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467127e98eaaa38f320e237706754e5a4928591c","tid":98602,"uid":46036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"唔小心入左黎 我翻出去先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf433eca3c2ca32ed8dfe17336a850134237c35","tid":98602,"uid":78887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"當佢嘟起個嘴仔同我講野<br />\n主動橋對手喺我膊頭攬住我 留意唔係普通橋住條腰<br />\n<br />\n對佢黎講我諗係晚晚傾電話tum訓覺同埋陪佢做佢中意嘅事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想聽下你嘅版本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b0815f1cc2c00a446a0251050e0bef9db85734","tid":98602,"uid":15800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:29:54.000Z","msg":"一齊扮狗扮貓<br />\n搭電梯既時候佢企落一級，然後攬實<br />\n每次返屋企都會目送到睇唔到佢為止<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知係咪一齊得耐左，佢依家好少主動攬我錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a24d631106fc99aa779ce175c33963ab683912","tid":98602,"uid":70940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊扮狗扮貓<br />\n搭電梯既時候佢企落一級，然後攬實<br />\n每次返屋企都會目送到睇唔到佢為止<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知係咪一齊得耐左，佢依家好少主動攬我錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會好唔知醜咁隊塊面埋去 叫佢錫我一啖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a6a3e0017196f7e05aff381d8abd8d55b55bef","tid":98602,"uid":11539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:49:41.000Z","msg":"佢蕩失路我會去搵佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過都就廿一年都未搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d5fda3b40177e4cbad39e0c167ff13fe6657c7","tid":98602,"uid":71888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲記得當日我着高跟鞋着到好痛 你公主抱我行咗好耐仲比咗對鞋我着 自己赤腳行<br />\n你射罰球前我會舉起我地手既暗號 然後你會再做個手勢回應我 打完比賽抱起錫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠都唔發我脾氣 我做錯事時你會抱起我打屁股 解釋比我知我做錯咩<br />\n帶我做唔同既運動 教我新既野<br />\n好錫我屋企人 <br />\n為咗我地既將來一齊努力 互相依賴<br />\n一齊咗四年一直咁愛我保護我珍惜我<br />\n我真係修咗幾世既福"},{"pid":"080cacd4ea3daf2f98c3eb94ebff7a523ed673f4","tid":98602,"uid":68093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"一齊係同一個馬桶上痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj